    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with various surface scratches and a few minor dings, while the interior has some visible wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
