    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic ride! This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and offers a smooth, reliable driving experience that you're going to love. It has been cared for properly, featuring a clean interior and a dependable engine that's ready for many more miles. It's a great choice for anyone seeking a quality car at a fair price!",
